    • Product

      public Product(Integer productId, String productName, Integer productPrice, String productDescription, boolean available, Integer availableQuantity, boolean discountCodeActive)
      A Product Item that will be created by GUI and then sent to the database.
      Parameters:
      associatedSellerId - The Seller ID.
      productName - The Product Name.
      productPrice - the Product Price.
      productDescription - The Product description.
      available - If available or not.
      availableQuantity - The available quantity.
      discountCodeActive - If a discount code exists for the product.
